-s-4hana-rise-and-grow-with-sap-successfactors-concur-ariba-btp-24-7-enterprise-managed-services-with-10-000-users-on-cover-sap-gold-partner ax-t" style="left:0.0vw;top:0.2323vw;width:19.7569vw;height:5.2083vw;font-family:'Nunito Sans',sans-serif;font-size:0.7292vw;font-weight:400;line-height:1.0417vw;color:#6b7280;text-align:left">RISE for the enterprise. GROW in 12 weeks for the mid-market. AMS reimagined with AXIOM. Gold Partner. Rising Star 2022.</p></div><div class="ax-component-4" style="left:1.9271vw;top:14.774vw;width:8.0729vw;height:1.7188vw"><p class="ax-text ax-t" style="left:0.0vw;top:0.7812vw;width:8.0729vw;height:0.9375vw;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:0.7292vw;font-weight:600;line-height:0.9494vw;color:#295da0;text-align:left;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center">Explore SAP services →</p></div><div class="ax-before" style="left:0.0521vw;top:0.0521vw;width:23.4896vw;height:0.1562vw;opacity:0.0;background-image:linear-gradient(90deg, #ee5a24 0%, #295da0 100%)"></div></div><div class="ax-component-15" style="left:24.4444vw;top:0.0vw;width:23.6111vw;height:19.4792vw;border-radius:1.0417vw;border:0.0521vw solid #e5e7eb;box-sizing:border-box;overflow:hidden;background-color:#ffffff"><span class="ax-div-trinity-card-icon" style="left:1.9271vw;top:2.1354vw;width:2.5vw;height:2.5vw;border-radius:0.625vw;display:block"><svg class="ax-ico" viewBox="0 0 48.0 48.0" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" preserveAspectRatio="none"><path transform="translate(12.0 16.0)" d="M19.35 6.04C18.67 2.59 15.64 0 12 0C9.11 0 6.6 1.64 5.35 4.04C2.34 4.36 0 6.91 0 10C0 13.31 2.69 16 6 16L19 16C21.76 16 24 13.76 24 11C24 8.36 21.95 6.22 19.35 6.04ZM19 14L6 14C3.79 14 2 12.21 2 10C2 7.79 3.79 6 6 6L6.71 6C7.37 3.69 9.48 2 12 2C15.04 2 17.5 4.46 17.5 7.5L17.5 8L19 8C20.66 8 22 9.34 22 11C22 12.66 20.66 14 19 14Z" fill="#20416c" fill-rule="nonzero"/></svg></span><div class="ax-div-trinity-card-eyebrow" style="left:1.9271vw;top:5.1198vw;widt