ght:2.2906vw"><p class="ax-xpense-supplierx-orderx-logystix-manufex-aeonxiq-production-grade-platforms-for-spend-procurement-distribution-logistics-manufacturing-and-enterprise-intelligence-sap-integrated-cloud-native-audit-ready ax-t" style="left:0.0vw;top:0.2073vw;width:20.3819vw;height:2.0833vw;font-family:'Nunito Sans',sans-serif;font-size:0.7292vw;font-weight:400;line-height:1.0417vw;color:#6b7280;text-align:left;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center">A 5-level autonomy engine for SAP AMS. 70% of L1 tickets close themselves at Level 4. Customer holds the dial.</p></div><div class="ax-component-4" style="left:1.9271vw;top:11.6474vw;width:5.3646vw;height:1.7031vw"><p class="ax-text ax-t" style="left:0.0vw;top:0.7656vw;width:5.3646vw;height:0.9375vw;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:0.7292vw;font-weight:600;line-height:0.9494vw;color:#295da0;text-align:left;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center">See the suite →</p></div><div class="ax-before" style="left:0.0521vw;top:0.0521vw;width:23.4896vw;height:0.1562vw;opacity:0.0;background-image:linear-gradient(90deg, #ee5a24 0%, #295da0 100%)"></div></div></div></div></section>
