2e;text-align:left;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center">Industry blueprints. Not generic playbooks.</h2></div><div class="ax-p-section-subhead" style="left:0.0vw;top:5.7292vw;width:35.4167vw;height:2.9167vw"><p class="ax-transformation-programmes-that-ignore-sector-economics-ship-late-and-miss-the-p-l-our-blueprints-are-written-by-vertical-the-exact-sap-modules-cloud-patterns-and-saas-products-that-move-that-sector-s-numbers ax-t" style="left:0.0vw;top:0.0vw;width:72.9167vw;height:2.9167vw;font-family:'Nunito Sans',sans-serif;font-size:0.9375vw;font-weight:400;line-height:1.4583vw;color:#526077;text-align:left;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center">Transformation programmes that ignore sector economics ship late and miss the P&amp;L. Our blueprints are written by vertical — the exact SAP modules, cloud patterns, and SaaS products that move that sector&#x27;s numbers.</p></div></div></div><span class="ax-line-6" style="left:80.2604vw;top:34.6875vw;width:0.0vw;height:29.2708vw;border:0.0521vw solid #eceef2;box-sizing:border-box;display:block"><svg class="ax-ico" viewBox="0 0 0.0 562.0" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" preserveAspectRatio="none"><path transform="translate(0.0 0.0)" d="M0 0L0 0.5L562 0.5L562 0L562 -0.5L0 -0.5L0 0Z" fill="#eceef2"/></svg></span></section>
